#### Smoothing Amount to round corners and smooth geometry (NBpts)  
Rounded corners can be cut faster, but check tolerances (see next)

#### Smoothing Step size (STEP)  
Rounding Error is roughly (Parameter 221 * Parameter 222) / 3
#### Smoothing vectors per second -- leave this at 800 (Umax)

#### Smoothing Centripetal options:  
0 = All axes and NO checking for excess accel  
-1 = Linear axes only and NO checking for excess accel  
-2 = All axes WITH checking for excess accel  
-3 = Linear axes only WITH checking for excess accel

#### Smoothing Filter half-width for feature detection (W)  
Increase this value to smooth over small glitches in your gcode programs

#### Smoothing Minimum angle for feature detection (Min_Angle)  
Machine will round corners that are wider than this angle

#### Smoothing S-Curve Filter Multiplier (S Curve)  
Set this to 0 to turn off S-Curve, 1 for full S-Curve, Between 0 and 1 for partial

#### Smoothing Movements Drawn in Backplot  
Set this to 1 to use Smoothing for Backplotting (slows it down considerably)

#### Smoothing Curve Feedrate Multiplier  
Increase this value to make your machine run faster (but bang more) -- 1 is normal

#### Smoothing Acceleration Multiplier  
Increase this value to make your machine accelerate faster than normal -- 1 is normal
